size=Geben Sie die maximale Größe von E-Mail Anhängen in MB an, die im Webaccess hochgeladen werden können.
limit=This limits the maximum disk usage for each user in MB.
mysql_database=This database will be created if it doesn't exists. To do this the user needs the right permissions.
mysql_password=This is the password that is set on the database. You need to set this password manually.
mysql_user=This is the username that will be used for connecting to database. The user has to be created and have the permissions to use the given database.
